Package: SCRAP
Type: Package
Title: Scraping function for Paying Attention to Attention research project
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anthony Ramos, Simon Munzert, Pablo Barbera
Maintainer: Anthony Ramos <ramosaj@usc.edu>
Description: This package provides a series of functions to download and parse URLs consumed by panelists in our research project and to scrape front pages of online news outlets
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests: testthat
Depends: rvest,
        boilerpipeR,
        urltools,
        stringr,
        digest,
        readr
